士"},{"pid":"a64aa6529e54f329234da39cd7764a343afe5caf","tid":1814244,"uid":5408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:04:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1e6a330861fe1c083b39af12094c8d11750ed3c7","tid":1814244,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041c1e2f6bcfd228dedda9a052087a5be0a2d45d","tid":1814244,"uid":23832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:08:11.000Z","msg":"推你老母個爛臭閪<br />\nPish"},{"pid":"01adc06999a27779d95da7343579bc32fc9c4d01","tid":1814244,"uid":69334,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:11:28.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係捉手足先有問題，裝修完全無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過有啲大偵探覺得裝修捉到鬼已經係破左大案咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n------------<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港獨立 唯一出路</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新症正名：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>中國肺炎</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d655f5ffd9a1c58e2610a28e6938d7ce4fb9c2e","tid":1814244,"uid":269159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:18:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n雖然提早終止遊行 無行過好唔夠皮 下次吹雞更加想出黎<br />\n重申 不分化不遣責不割蓆不篤灰"},{"pid":"e5ee47d81de062d331081490101da60226b32be2","tid":1814244,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d655f5ffd9a1c58e2610a28e6938d7ce4fb9c2e","tid":1814244,"uid":269159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:18:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n雖然提早終止遊行 無行過好唔夠皮 下次吹雞更加想出黎<br />\n重申 不分化不遣責不割