ree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb543cf6ec1036ab4bec29e39b52b456d8f8e74","tid":1814244,"uid":53016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:37:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用理論分析<br />\n<br />\n如果係真前線，你咁鬼多事扮柯南走上前去查案，通常都無任何辨証方法結果就係搵記者黎，引到記者鏡頭影到你個樣同前線有交談，班狗睇cctv你係案發現場以為你係同檔可能直接濫捕埋你自找麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n如果真係係鬼，佢目的不外乎賊贓嫁禍制造機會提早清場，就算比你斷正隻鬼有槍有警棍，你行埋隻鬼到爭執、捉鬼、屌狗，結果班狗都係一樣直接濫捕你。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以結論最好就係見到裝修就保持距離食花生，河水不犯井水築人牆人鍊隔開阻止其他人、鬼、臥底挑起事端搞大件事，要靜靜雞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當日有兩單，另一單係100%捉錯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">理得佢鬼唔鬼都費鬼事分，總之邊個阻前線裝修藍店、紅店，&mdash;律當阻膠處理拖走佢</span></span>"},{"pid":"b28d4eaedd35c8aeb187025f3e3e5063c6dd5c0c","tid":1814244,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:39:50.000Z","msg":"推熱門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc873ffc24db96205654aba9503ee4248caf8d2","tid":1814244,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"推熱門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c145c8da30346b98688860a6b2c39a872e75e6","tid":1814244,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:40:37.000Z","msg":"係，不過最心痛就係俾仆街便衣狗搞手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a8871e93c9886c72c46968735c42a7d35f24eb","tid":1814244,"uid":55197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:41:57.000Z","msg":"不分化、不捉鬼、不篤灰、不割蓆，天滅中共，黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmo